            CLAIM.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="terms-indemnity">
          <h2 id="terms-indemnity">9) Indemnification</h2>
          <p>
            You agree to indemnify and hold harmless JHD and its licensors from any claims, losses, and expenses (including
            reasonable attorneys' fees) arising from your violation of these Terms or misuse of the apps.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="terms-termination">
          <h2 id="terms-termination">10) Termination</h2>
          <p>
            We may suspend or terminate access if you breach these Terms. You may uninstall or discontinue use at any time; this
            does not entitle you to refunds beyond each platform's policies.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="terms-changes">
          <h2 id="terms-changes">11) Changes to These Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We may update these Terms as the apps evolve. The "Last Updated" date will change when the Terms change,
            and we may provide additional notice where required or appropriate. Continued use after updates means you
            accept the updated Terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="terms-governing-law">
