            These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of Delaware, USA, without regard to its conflict of laws rules. Venue
            for disputes shall be the state or federal courts located in Delaware, where permissible.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section" aria-labelledby="terms-app-store">
          <h2 id="terms-app-store">13) Platform Store Requirements</h2>
          <p>
